Class CavityWithLastCorrectionTableModel

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
org.jlab.phaser.swing.table.CavityWithLastCorrectionTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
OrderedCavityWithLastCorrectionTableModel
public class CavityWithLastCorrectionTableModel extends AbstractTableModel
A table model for holding cavities by name and last correction date, and which relies on the view (JTable) to handle dynamic sorting.
